==Notes==
# Or circa [[520]].  [[Google]] returns 148 results for Creoda being born c. 540 [http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&lr=&safe=off&as_qdr=all&q=creoda+540&btnG=Search] and 136 results for his birth at c. 520 [http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&lr=&safe=off&as_qdr=all&q=creoda+520&btnG=Search]. c. 520 is relatively implausible given that his father, Cynewald, was born c. 512.

